# VIRL — Cost, Performance, and Freshness Backlog

**For Claude Code  ·  Post-Intelligence-Sharpening  ·  Optimization phase**

Post-INTEL-4, plan generation produces richer outputs (slides arrays, story frames, long-form bodies) at higher cost and latency. Hotfix #73 bumped `maxTokens` to 12000 to stop truncation. This backlog captures the optimizations that bring spend and latency back down without walking back the value.

